<div type="elementDocumentation" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="signature">
    <head>
        
        <!-- PREMIS Semantic unit 1.8.1 -->
        <abbr>1.8.1</abbr>
        <gi>signature</gi>
        
    </head>
    
    <div type="semanticcomponents">
        <!-- PREMIS Semantic components -->
        <p>signatureEncoding</p>
        <p>signer</p>
        <p>signatureMethod</p>
        <p>signatureValue</p>
        <p>signatureValidationRules</p>
        <p>signatureProperties</p>
        <p>keyInformation</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="definition">
        <!-- PREMIS Definition -->
        <p>Information needed to use a digital signature to authenticate the signer
            of an object and/or the information contained in the object.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="rationale">
        <!-- PREMIS Rationale -->
        <p>A repository may have a policy of generating digital signatures for files
            on ingest, or may have a need to store and later validate incoming
            digital signatures.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="usagenotes">
